<H3> <TI>   Secretary Jiang Zemin Inspects Zhuhai Enterprises </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Secretary Jiang Zemin Inspects Zhuhai Enterprises </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    Guangdong's Xie Fei Accompanies Jiang </H4>

<F P=102> HK1906033594 Hong Kong TA KUNG PAO in Chinese 19 Jun 94 p 2 </F>
<F P=103> HK1906033594 </F>
<F P=104>  Hong Kong TA KUNG PAO </F>
<F P=105>  Chinese </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [Report: "Jiang Zemin Inspects Zhuhai"] </F>
  [Text] Zhuhai (TA KUNG PAO) -- Central Committee General 
Secretary Jiang Zemin is now on an inspection tour of Zhuhai. 
  Accompanied by Guangdong CPC Committee Secretary Xie Fei and 
Zhuhai Mayor Liang Guangda on the afternoon of 17 June, Jiang 
Zemin inspected a series of large enterprises in Zhuhai, 
including Asia Simulation, Geli Air Conditioning, and the Giant 
Group. Jiang Zemin continued his inspection of Zhuhai on 18 
June, and made arrangements to meet with some of Zhuhai's 
entrepreneurs in the evening. 
  President Jiang Zemin inspected Zhuhai four years ago. He is 
staying at Zhuhai's Shijing Mountain Villa during his current 
trip, just as he did during his previous trip. 

