over 500 years ago in the Ming Dynasty, and mounted the rostrum 
of Tiananmen, where the late Chairman Mao Zedong announced the 
founding of the People's Republic of China in 1949. 
  Yesterday Estrada watched a military display performed by 
the 
people's armed police near the capital airport. 

