  [Text] Beijing, June 22 (XINHUA) -- A friendship delegation 
from the People's Liberation Army (PLA) led by Commander of the 
Chengdu Military Area Command General Li Jiulong left Kunming 
city today for Myanmar [Burma] and Laos on a goodwill visit at 
the invitation of the Myanmar Ministry of Defence and the Lao 
