<F P=106> [By reporter Shi Tao (4258 3447)] </F>
  [Text] Changsha, 21 Jun (XINHUA) -- Wen Jiabao, alternate 
member of the CPC Central Committee's Political Bureau and 
member of the Secretariat, and a central work group led by him 
arrived in Changsha today to provide guidelines for Hunan's 
